
            Video
            Woman in Pakistan paraded naked through village streets
            A woman has been stripped naked and paraded through her village in Pakistan.  The people who assaulted her accused one of her sons of having an affair.Speaking to the BBC, Shahnaz Bibi says she cried and pleaded with the men, who she says continued to beat her.Aleem Maqbool reports. 
                
                        20 Jun 2011
                    
                
        
